A great all round truck, with many new upgrades for 2013 to make them even better. Uses standard 8mm axels, heat treated for your pleasure. 

WHEELS
SEISMIC HOT SPOT 66*49MM PURPLE:
The idea behind the 66mm Seismic Hot Spots is that Seismic wanted to create a fast and nimble wheel that will also grip the asphalt. The Seismic urethane is simply fast and grippy! . Seismic hot spot its  an amazing wheel for your mini that will get you around town in a jiffy!

Solid oak

TRUCKS

Really quick response. Great for those tiny old school boards.

WHEELS
SEISMIC RIPPLER 59*43MM PURPLE
Something has been missing from the world of longboard and carving wheels: a shape with classic grip-oriented lip profiles in a size under 60mm. I. The Rippler makes a great all-around wheel for mini cruisers and retro pool/park boards
An unbeatable filmer wheel, too!
